message: To get a score of 100, combine two liquids: one 'extracted' and one 'filtered'. The vial tool works on 'solid' ingredients (magical or mundane) to produce 'extracted' liquids (value 30). The filter tool works on 'gas' ingredients (magical or mundane) or 'liquid, mundane' ingredients to produce 'filtered' liquids (value 30). The highest value (100) is achieved by combining a 'liquid, extracted, magical' with a 'liquid, filtered, mundane' OR a 'liquid, extracted, mundane' with a 'liquid, filtered, magical'. Be careful: vial on liquid items, or filter on solid items, generally results in negative value items.
